\begin_layout Note
In Bayesian Stats, learning (or quantifying uncertainty about) parameter
 of interest 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 under the presence of a nuisance parameter 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\in\Lambda$
\end_inset

