 prior 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{d}\Pi(\phi,\lambda)$
\end_inset

 with PDF/PMF 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi(\phi,\lambda)=\pi(\phi|\lambda)\pi(\lambda)$
\end_inset

 on the joint space of ALL Your unknown parameters 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta=(\phi,\lambda)^{\top}$
\end_inset

; you compute the joint posterior distribution 
